## VM Args Template for Static Port Mode E2E Tests
## Variables: {{NODE_NAME}}, {{DIST_PORT}}, {{COOKIE}}

-sname {{NODE_NAME}}
-setcookie {{COOKIE}}

## Disable standard EPMD
-start_epmd false

## Use static port EPMD module
-epmd_module gsmlg_epmd_static

## Distribution port (same for all nodes in static mode)
-erl_epmd_port {{DIST_PORT}}

## Kernel configuration
-kernel inet_dist_listen_min {{DIST_PORT}}
-kernel inet_dist_listen_max {{DIST_PORT}}

## Code paths
-pa {{CODE_PATHS}}

## Test-specific settings
+P 1048576
+Q 1048576
